metadata.name: Dingly #1
metadata.description: Dingly NFT is a collection of one-of-a-kind Profile Pictures (PFPs) that are stored and traded as non-fungible tokens (NFTs) on the Ethereum blockchain. Each PFP is hand drawn, and the NFT represents ownership of the digital PFP. With Dingly NFT, you can own a unique and personalized digital profile picture that is truly yours, and trade it just like a physical piece of art
